{"tid":1211680,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"原來連毅進文憑個英文名都係用普通話拼音","createTime":"2019-06-12T16:18:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T07:56:32.000Z","uid":2186,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"78170ecf7a8190aecc1074c4768ea8fd2e3e9ae0","tid":1211680,"uid":2186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T16:18:10.000Z","msg":"毅進文憑（dipolma Yi Jin )<br />\n有理由懷疑個dipolma 都唔撚係比香港人讀<br />\n唔怪得知 d毅進狗打香港人打得咁狠 原來都唔撚係香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c456eec6f370de52b6d02b72790b40f123dcfebe","tid":1211680,"uid":165336,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:09:46.000Z","msg":"明明以前係叫Project Yi Jin<br />\n小小分享...我以前都讀過毅進<br />\n發現讀紀律部隊既人最冇紀律<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己本身讀書唔掂<br />\n都好驚入到毅進仔多數同學都係死mk<br />\n我中學都成日俾人洽<br />\n入得毅進除左讀唔到書又想升學<br />\n就係唔撚讀書又冇咩特別興趣想發展<br />\n遇到d mk點算<br />\n好彩我果班d人個個都幾nice<br />\n有d仲係退休人士搵d野黎讀下<br />\n但係讀紀律部隊果d學生<br />\n個樣都特別mk,行過走廊講野都大大聲<br />\n轉堂轉課室如果上一手係紀律部隊班上堂<br />\n間房多數都係亂撚哂,仲要好多種氣味<br />\n止汗劑,食物,飲品,痴撚線我果班d人從來唔會上堂食野<br />\n食都係小小地,唔會搞到間房有味,<br />\n佢地肯定開餐咁撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有陣時如果隔離房係紀律部隊班,會成日聽到d人係打牆<br />\n砰砰聲,有一次砰得太勁<br />\n個miss話唔好理佢地啦<br />\n我果班有個大隻佬同miss講<br />\nmiss你等等,然後起身一拳車落幅牆度<br />\n大力過對面好多,驚撚死對面<br />\n之後成堂都靜哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家d死黑警成日俾人叫毅進仔<br />\n毅進計劃同讀過毅進既人真係多撚謝佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2369aa79628149d422562c1bc7b280023366612","tid":1211680,"uid":69314,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:11:42.000Z","msg":"大家有共識行動，請幫手推<br />\n<br />\n613行動部署<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1212252\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1212252</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3e9c31aff6d664f213296f7a3a73a5190c94b982","tid":1211680,"uid":135445,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T21:02:17.000Z","msg":"班偽進狗<br />\n讀唔成書咪做暴徒囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c26ece41a26a570e627eacdf54b6928514b0509","tid":1211680,"uid":224351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:56:32.000Z","msg":"[img]&lt;div class=&quot;tenor-gif-embed&quot; data-postid=&quot;10396170&quot; data-share-method=&quot;host&quot; data-width=&quot;100%&quot; data-aspect-ratio=&quot;2.388059701492537&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;<a href=\"https://tenor.com/view/ben-stiller-diet-coke-gif-10396170&quot;&gt;Ben\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftenor.com%2Fview%2Fben-stiller-diet-coke-gif-10396170%22%3EBen&d=o1jNmZJj5m3DpFdm5BDgvwy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=c0d5043b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tenor.com/view/ben-stiller-diet-coke-gif-10396170&quot;&gt;Ben</a> Stiller Diet Coke GIF&lt;/a&gt; from &lt;a href=&quot;<a href=\"https://tenor.com/search/benstiller-gifs&quot;&gt;Benstiller\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftenor.com%2Fsearch%2Fbenstiller-gifs%22%3EBenstiller&d=o1jNmZJj5m3DpFdm5BDgvwy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=b8067671\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tenor.com/search/benstiller-gifs&quot;&gt;Benstiller</a> GIFs&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;script type=&quot;text/javascript&quot; async src=&quot;<a href=\"https://tenor.com/embed.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftenor.com%2Fembed.js%22%3E%3C%2Fscript%3E%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=o1jNmZJj5m3DpFdm5BDgvwy7V